- C√≥ 2 lo·∫°i:
‚ù§Ô∏è Transaction-scoped persistence context:
	G·∫Øn li·ªÅn v·ªõi m·ªôt transaction (persistence context ƒë∆∞·ª£c t·∫°o khi transaction b·∫Øt ƒë·∫ßu v√† b·ªã h·ªßy khi transaction k·∫øt th√∫c (commit/rollback))
