	C√≥ th·ªÉ persist entity m√† kh√¥ng c·∫ßn transaction, nh∆∞ng kh√¥ng th·ªÉ flush n·∫øu kh√¥ng c√≥ transaction.
‚ö†Ô∏è Trong Stateless Session Bean, extended persistence context c·ªßa m·ªói component l√† ƒë·ªôc l·∫≠p.
